column2: SELECT TOP #      s.ra, s.dec,      s.z,      g.h_alpha_flux, g.h_alpha_flux_err,   g.h_beta_flux, g.h_beta_flux_err,   g.oiii_#_flux, g.oiii_#_flux_err,    g.nii_#_flux, g.nii_#_flux_err,   g.sii_#_flux, g.sii_#_flux_err,   g.sii_#_flux, g.sii_#_flux_err,        g.h_alpha_reqw, g.h_alpha_reqw_err,   g.oiii_#_reqw, g.oiii_#_reqw_err,         e.bptclass,         p.modelMag_u, p.modelMag_g, p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_z,   p.modelMagErr_u, p.modelMagErr_g, p.modelMagErr_r, p.modelMagErr_i, p.modelMagErr_z,         p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z,      s.class, s.subClass  from galSpecLine AS g        JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid     JOIN galSpecExtra AS e ON e.specobjid = g.specobjid     JOIN SpecPhotoAll AS p ON p.specobjid = g.specobjid  WHERE      abs(g.oiii_#_flux / g.oiii_#_flux_err) < #   AND abs(g.nii_#_flux  / g.nii_#_flux_err)  < #   AND abs(g.h_beta_flux    / g.h_beta_flux_err)    < #   AND abs(g.h_alpha_flux   / g.h_alpha_flux_err)   < #         AND s.class         = &&&   AND s.zwarning       = #
